StringValues.16: A note left by one of the High Queen's Scouts

Pages.Text: I have had to slay a number of Olthoi on my journey down here and find that the ones inhabiting these lairs now are more dangerous than the Olthoi we understood to live here. The catacombs have been expanded.  The Queen must be made aware of this.  I leave this note in case I am unable to report.
